+ /***********************************************************************
+  *
+  *	Definitions for various path related things.  These are compiled into
+  *	the GNU Smalltalk interpreter and are used for finding various files
+  *	(the image file, the kernel .st files, etc.).
+  *
+  ***********************************************************************/
+ 
